channel.title: Song Name Competition!
channel.description: I know that there are too many competitions going at the moment, but I am going to be hosting a song name competition! I have run out of ideas for names and I don't want to end up calling it something like 'banana'. This thread is also kind of a 'tracks/collaborations' thread because I will be happy to accept any feedback on the song. The link to the song is: **https://soundcloud.com/user-460338301/random-song**. Rules: Have fun! :wink:
